{"tid":1809992,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［一萬蚊］豪門苟芸慧搲完婚紗贊助唔落credit 設計師心血慘批垃圾！！！","createTime":"2020-01-03T13:09:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T18:10:50.000Z","uid":56716,"like":20,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0196a0de1af8a7bac39126b33579e02fc5d5aa8a","tid":1809992,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T13:09:32.000Z","msg":"事緣肥苟結婚搲設計師kev贊助婚紗，kev以專業角度認為香檳粉紅色比較適合苟，但苟要營造「美女與野獸」嘅主題，指定要黃色裙，其野獸老公曾作出承諾會落credit，事後反口不特止，肥苟仲周圍唱kev的設計為「垃圾」！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乜肥苟你唔係嫁咗入豪門咩？連婚紗都要搲贊助你醜唔醜呀？事後仲唱人垃圾，你把口仲臭過我吉野妹！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BdgkRus.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBdgkRus.jpg&h=3116e52b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oryfFqj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2ForyfFqj.jpg&h=618abdd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「苟姑娘的夢想婚禮是以「童話故事」為主題，初時曾遭William嫌棄幼稚，但當William聽到未婚妻話兩人由相識到拍拖，再邁向人生新一篇，感覺如童話故事的男女主角一樣時，William就改變初衷，為苟姑娘安排童話式婚禮，兩人就做童話中的「公主」和「王子」。 」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181013/mobile/bkn-20181013124803140-1013_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181013%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181013124803140-1013_00862_001.html&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7Kcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=3b3b0fcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181013/mobile/bkn-20181013124803140-1013_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">得喇最靚係你喇，結婚結到要抬高自己「美女」角色，醜化老公為「野獸」。咁多童話故事唔揀，係要揀美女與野獸，又唔見你揀灰姑娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />哎喲差啲唔記得添，有人初出道時「一萬蚊」做爛市添，台妹急功近利唔知價，以為萬萬聲好多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"a9a7147590bb76b88e02fda7ac60ea18c2156a0e","tid":1809992,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T13:14:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/14/203541_a8ac365d26b76baa047471ff5ad50bfd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F14%2F203541_a8ac365d26b76baa047471ff5ad50bfd.png&h=0f87a7d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/14/203543_3685689a02c2471197bf4a33279e0221.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F14%2F203543_3685689a02c2471197bf4a33279e0221.png&h=2fee6561&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n選美出身嘅苟芸慧，出道多年，代表作欠奉，最為人津津樂道是她突然暴漲嘅身型及緋聞。被傳曾介入郭富城與熊黛琳嘅戀情令兩人分手，又曾與楊受成兒子楊政龍傳緋聞，入行初期與有錢仔藝人羅天宇拍拖，更曾硬撬朱璇有米男友令姊妹反目。一向有鋪釣金龜癮嘅苟姑娘，得償所願搭上聖安娜創辦人兒子陸漢洋，現已嫁入豪門。"},{"pid":"ab1653a5de9dfa5f5a5d0c8cd5c395211b6d92a8","tid":1809992,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T13:25:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">羅天宇苟芸慧同居不同床致分手</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"144346ff82ac67165261df0be19f833f37dcf6cc","tid":1809992,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab1653a5de9dfa5f5a5d0c8cd5c395211b6d92a8","tid":1809992,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T13:25:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">羅天宇苟芸慧同居不同床致分手</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T13:26:29.000Z","msg":"掠完水又唔比屌係咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c1bf135be9f320296d42c7ed602604edbbe791","tid":1809992,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"144346ff82ac67165261df0be19f833f37dcf6cc","tid":1809992,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab1653a5de9dfa5f5a5d0c8cd5c395211b6d92a8","tid":1809992,"uid":71166,"like":0